Title: Death to the Living
Description:
Now it's time for them to pay. They'll wish they never set foot in our lands and threatened our home.

We will drive them out, we will drive them into the ground, and we will leave them to rot.
ObjectivesText: Kill every Scarlet that has a beating heart.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Meet Lilian Voss outside Fenris Keep.

Objectives.Text: Meet Lilian Voss Ouside Fenris Keep
